data.description: Gorgeous Doublewide on 2.28 Acres! Bright open floor plan with lots of room for entertaining. Kitchen has lots of cabinet and countertop space w/ a center island for extra prep room for cooking. Spacious Master bedroom and Master Bathroom has double vanities and Roman soaking tub. Relax by the fireplace and enjoy the panoramic views from your Family Room. Beautiful private cleared and wooded land with plenty of room for your animals and toys. Workshop/Utility shed to store your tools or turn into a work area. This one is to good to pass up.
